docs.lead_paragraph: LA PAZ, Bolivia, Jan. 20 (AP).--The Bolivian Foreign Office issued a communique today blaming Paraguayan soldiers for the sanguinary clash on Thursday on the BolivianParaguayan border. It declared that fifteen Bolivian cavalrymen repulsed a force four times as large, losing one man.
